1) changes:
   *) refinement crest method: besides user-given 2 other sweep directions included
   *) inclusion further clarification in the SWAN Implementation Manual with
      respect to running SWAN using OpenMP built with the Intel Fortran
      compiler (see Ch. 5)

2) bug fixes:
   *) prevention friction velocity from dropping to zero at very large wind speeds
      in wind drag formulation Zijlema et al. (2012)
   *) correction adaptation of units of some output quantities in case of true energy
   *) correction transformation in output wind vector

